              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1405967-lavinia?shelf=2009">2009</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1405967-lavinia?shelf=journals-biographies-memoirs">journals-biographies-memoirs</a>
